Description
-----------

This command toggles between all the possible values for the specified CVar.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    toggle [CVar]

Parameters
----------

-   [CVar] - The CVar to toggle.

Notes
-----

This console command is useful in conjunction with the [bind](Bind_%28console_command%29 "Bind (console command)") console command. It makes it possible to toggle a CVar on and off with a single key press.

